---
import GeneratorLayout from "../layouts/GeneratorLayout.astro";
---

<GeneratorLayout
    title="Privacy Policy - zygote.ro"
    description="Privacy Policy for zygote.ro. We prioritize your privacy with client-side only generation tools."
>
    <div class="content-limit">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 18, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose">
            <p>
                At <strong>zygote.ro</strong>, we take your privacy seriously.
                This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when
                you use our website.
            </p>

            <h2>1. No Data Collection</h2>
            <p>
                The core functionality of our generators runs entirely in your
                web browser (client-side).
                <strong
                    >We do not transmit, store, or process your input data on
                    our servers.</strong
                >
                Any project names, code snippets, or configuration details you enter
                remain on your device.
            </p>

            <h2>2. Analytics</h2>
            <p>
                We use <strong>Google Analytics 4 (GA4)</strong> to understand how
                visitors interact with our website to improve the user experience.
                Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymous data such as:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Pages you visit and how much time you spend on them</li>
                <li>Your approximate location (e.g., country or city)</li>
                <li>The device and browser you are using</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                We do not collect any Personally Identifiable Information (PII)
                through Google Analytics. IP addresses are processed by Google
                but are not logged or stored.
            </p>

            <h2>3. External Links</h2>
            <p>
                Our website may contain links to external sites (e.g., GitHub,
                documentation). We are not responsible for the privacy practices
                of these external sites.
            </p>

            <h2>4. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will
                notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on
                this page.
            </p>

            <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a
                    href="/contact">contact us</a
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</GeneratorLayout>

<style>
    .content-limit {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .last-updated {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--color-subtle);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .prose p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--color-muted-foreground);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    a {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    strong {
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-weight: 600;
    }
</style>
